      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must have a Parivar Pehchan Patra (PPP).\n1. The construction of new grow-out ponds subsidy will be provided by the State Government for the expansion of fisheries in various urban/semi-urban areas only under the construction of new grow-out ponds under the Pradhan Mantri Matasya Sampada Yojana (PMMSY) scheme.\n1. Central financial assistance for the construction of new grow-out ponds will be provided only for the ponds prepared for fisheries.\n1. The applicant should have own land with clear title or having land on a long-term registered lease, not less than a minimum of 7 years.\n\n",
        "eligibilityDescription": [
